msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Hello?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu, yes?\r\nI was under the impression you left Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "The heir to the legacy of Lau Ka Long."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "So the Snake Flower Triad?\r\nWhat do you want?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "I was simply hoping to make\r\nan introduction in person."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Sorry, I'm not interested.\r\n...Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Up here, Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Do you remember this man?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Your advice had a great impact on him.\r\nHe came to me begging to back off the Saio Triad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "In other words, he chose to disobey my orders.\r\nAnd there is only one punishment for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Thanks to you, this man's life is forfeit.\r\nIf you want to stop me, go to where you last saw him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Come alone. I'll be waiting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "The last place I saw him...\r\nThat would be the Yoshida Batting Center."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "This is the place. The Snake Flower\r\nshould be waiting for me here…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "Hey, are you okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Somehow...\r\nThat you, Kiryu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "So the Snake Flower would do\r\nthis to one of their own?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "What about the man in the mask?\r\nWhere'd he go?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "Right here... Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "I'm surprised you came. I didn't imagine\r\nthis little punk would matter that much to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Is this really necessary?\r\nYou could've just talked to me from that screen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Yes, I can't deny that. However, I have\r\nsome people here I'd like you to meet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "These are the Snake Flower elite forces,\r\nsent directly from the homeland."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "They were quick to arrive when I told\r\nthem I could give them Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "You destroyed any hope we had of conquering Japan\r\nso many years ago. We cannot forgive that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "And yet, our moronic friend here had different ideas.\r\nHe wanted to let you go free."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "He claimed you weren't as bad as we said,\r\nalmost as though under the dragon's spell."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Between the screen hacking and the bomb placement,\r\nthough... nothing gets done unless <font_kind=yakuza_italic>I</font_kind> do it myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Pathetic, isn't it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "Couldn't say."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "No matter. After I finish you once and for all,\r\nthe Snake Flower Triad will take Kamurocho for good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "And then, I will cement my position as\r\nLau Ka Long's successor. I will reign supreme."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Sounds like I don't have to hold back, then.\r\nSomeone as supreme as you can handle anything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Very well.\r\nI'll show you what true pain feels like, Kiryu!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "I-I don't get it... This is impossible!\r\nThe Snake Flower was supposed to rise again...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "You sound ridiculous."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "I'd never lose to even your best.\r\nYour leadership needs to do the research."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "You have a lot to learn if you want to rebuild.\r\nTry following in the Saio Triad's footsteps."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "They had the foresight to weasel into\r\nKamurocho with hundreds of men."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Their boss is a strategic mastermind as well.\r\nHe's not a common thug like you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "What... did you call me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "You're just as soft as everyone says, Kiryu.\r\nYou really won't finish me off?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "If you let me leave here, you'll regret it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "You're in no position to be boasting.\r\nLook around you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Y-You...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "This traitor wanted to kill me.\r\nI saved because of you, Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "You think I moron, huh?\r\nYou think you so much smarter than me!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "H-Hold on a second.\r\nI didn't<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Shut your mouth!\r\nYou listen to me from now on!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu. Nothing good happens\r\nwhen my gang take you on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "To Snake Flower, you like poison."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Heh... True enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "We keep our heads down for little bit.\r\nI no kill this guy. Don't worry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Good. That's the right call.\r\nBye, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "If the Dragon of Dojima in Kamurocho,\r\nthe Saio be forced to leave someday."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Until then, we wait in shadows,\r\nbiding our time..."
msgstr ""

